{"tid":1742510,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美眾院通過參議院版本香港人權法案","createTime":"2019-11-20T22:57:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-20T23:50:13.000Z","uid":336583,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f702d177bcdae3d14cf636c0594609dc0c36bd3d","tid":1742510,"uid":336583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T22:57:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2309031\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Flanding%2FmobArticle2%2Fid%2F2309031&d=s5Gqkxkf8ApsCpMlSmcRzvFndj8FUwf2P%2BvTNEmbS2k%3D&h=4daeffb7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2309031</a><br />\n<br />\n美國眾議院周三通過參議院版本的《香港民主與人權法案》，下一步將呈交總統特朗普審批。不過，特朗普未表態會否簽署成為法律，抑或會否運用否決權否決法案。<br />\n<br />\n眾議院以壓倒性的412票對1票，通過《香港民主與人權法案》；該法案早一日已由參議院在無異議情況下通過。法案要求美國國務卿每年至少一次向國會證明香港擁有足夠自治權，有資格獲得美國授予的特殊貿易地位。法案還規定對在香港侵犯人權負有責任的中港官員進行制裁。<br />\n<br />\n眾議院周三亦通過法案，要求定期評估香港特殊金融地位；眾議院還準備就《禁止向香港出口防暴裝備法案》進行表決。<br />\n<br />\n有分析認為，中美貿易談判仍未達成協議，特朗普有意爭取兩國簽定貿協，以助他提升民望，贏得明年總統大選。如果特朗普簽署香港法案，勢必激怒北京政府，這將增加中美貿談難度。因此，特朗普可能陷入兩難局面。"},{"pid":"85454007131fa740568184a0901caa0f2a41c4c4","tid":1742510,"uid":336583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T22:58:00.000Z","msg":"邊個反對<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc1f7574be369bbd2197c3be10eefc34e2ed0442","tid":1742510,"uid":40667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T23:01:35.000Z","msg":"怏撚到？！"},{"pid":"f4714dde7780216a771cf2ebe0d3f0dd03fd291c","tid":1742510,"uid":184433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"85454007131fa740568184a0901caa0f2a41c4c4","tid":1742510,"uid":336583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T22:58:00.000Z","msg":"邊個反對<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T23:01:50.000Z","msg":"奶共狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c32b3ead54189e3dc45c11bc918b2c4ff7e84404","tid":1742510,"uid":184433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bc1f7574be369bbd2197c3be10eefc34e2ed0442","tid":1742510,"uid":40667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T23:01:35.000Z","msg":"怏撚到？！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T23:04:48.000Z","msg":"等當奴侵收埋個尾<br />\n<br />\nBtw 留名等睇口交部"},{"pid":"d4f211cd20beebc4150149d1ed8306514b5da8d4","tid":1742510,"uid":50124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f4714dde7780216a771cf2ebe0d3f0dd03fd291c","tid":1742510,"uid":184433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"85454007131fa740568184a0901caa0f2a41c4c4","tid":1742510,"uid":336583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T22:58:00.000Z","msg":"邊個反對<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T23:01:50.000Z","msg":"奶共狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T23:09:21.000Z","msg":"唔一定,有可能係唔鍾意參議院版本既"},{"pid":"e395c59b78c2f27b33983922a032ea8afdadf468","tid":1742510,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T23:50:13.000Z","msg":"法案正式在兩院通過！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1742532\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1742532</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n幫推，入去感謝參眾議員"}]}